  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to SpiderMonkey</title>

    <para><application>SpiderMonkey</application> is Mozilla's JavaScript engine
    written in C/C++. The most recent standalone source code release implements
    JavaScript 1.8.5.</para>

    &lfs70_built;

